When it’s time to host, we’ve got it handled. Whether it’s a relaxed lunch, a refined dinner, or an electrifying cocktail reception, our events team is here to make it happen. Expect nothing less than exceptional food and service that’ll elevate your event to the next level. Our team is ready to take care of everything — you focus on your guests, we’ll handle the rest. Located in the heart of Downtown Plant City,
Propagation Whiskey Bar & Kitchen
is a culinary gem rooted in bold flavors, thoughtful craft, and a whole lot of heart. Born from the team behind Roots, Propagation is where elevated food meets whiskey-forward hospitality — a space where comfort and creativity come together on every plate and in every glass.
Our menu is ingredient-driven, seasonally inspired, and built to showcase the best of local farms and Southern influence. From lunch through late night, we’re serving up dynamic dishes, signature cocktails, and an ever-growing whiskey list that now features over 250 bottles from around the world.
At Propagation, we’re all about good food, strong pours, and memorable moments — no pretension, just passion.
Come hungry, stay curious. We’re just getting started.
